### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@contentType = application/json

@token = Bearer {{token}}

### Get all posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Get post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Create a new post (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "excerpt": "This is a brief description of my first blog post",
  "content": "<h1>Welcome to My Blog</h1><p>This is the content of my first blog post. It contains HTML formatting.</p><ul><li>First point</li><li>Second point</li></ul>",
  "author": "John Doe",
  "tags": "react, javascript, tutorial"
}

###

### Update a post (requires token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Updated Blog Post Title",
  "excerpt": "Updated excerpt for the blog post",
  "content": "<h1>Updated Content</h1><p>This is the updated content of the blog post.</p>",
  "author": "John Doe",
  "tags": "react, javascript, tutorial, updated"
}

###

### Delete a post (requires token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###
